- First framework for a snowball-sampling strategy for identification and profiling of permanent policy partners - delivered;
- one) Questionnaire, to be distributed by the NEDB amongst the first stakeholders they invite to the policy dialogue, for collecting their suggestions on additional members, including names, position and contacts, to be invited to the policy dialogue elaborated;
- Final list of key stakeholders to be included in the policy process - delivered;
- Revisions of national legislation and international engagements of the country to inform an instrumental definition of social protection and its components accomplished - delivered;
- Data requirements and evidence that can inform the discussions around social protection with a focus on coverage, adequacy, comprehensiveness identified - delivered;
- mettings with the core stakeholders to validate the instrumental definition and its components - attended;
- Revision of the list of relevant stakeholders based on the instrumental definition and its components - accomplished;
- Preliminary meeting with the core stakeholders of the policy process to brainstorm on expectations and best practices, and to identify interesting, comparative case-studies that should be elaborated to inform the e-Workshops - held;
- series of online sessions totalling 2 days to explain the importance of a SPP, discuss the working definition of SP and its components - perfomed;
- preliminary meetings with core stakeholders to assess their views about the risks around the policy process that could prevent reaching intermediate goals and measures that could avoid or mitigating them - attended; 
- note detailing possible challenges in the process and ways to mitigate them - delivered;
- First draft of the roadmap to be shared with all stakeholders for comments and suggestions - concluded on November 2021;
- Final draft of the roadmap building from written comments on the first draft - concluded on Ocotober 2021;
- Final validation e-workshop to present the final version of the roadmap and plan the next steps - concluded on 28 Ocotober 2021.
